"|402x428","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-053.jpg?height=427&width=401&top__y=980&top__x=468","line":1060,"embedded":true},{"title":"|764x188","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-055.jpg?height=256&width=1043&top__y=1369&top__x=362","line":1091,"embedded":true},{"title":"0, \\frac{\\sqrt{5}}{5}\\.$ )；\n(4) $\\triangle F M N$ 周长的最小值为 $\\sqrt{2}+1$.\n\n其中正确结论的为（）\nA. (1)(2)\nB. (2)(3)\nC. (3)(4)\nD. (1)(4)\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-078.jpg?height=427&width=404&top__y=980&top__x=466","line":1534},{"title":"2,+\\infty)$\nD. $(-\\infty, 2) \\cup(2,+\\infty)$\n\n#### 10.2.2 【 练 1-1\n\n圆 $x^{2}+y^{2}+4 \\sin \\theta \\cdot x+4 \\cos \\theta \\cdot y+1=0$ 的半径等于 $\\qquad$ .\n\n#### 10.2.3 【 练 1-2\n\n已知 $A(-2,2) ， B(2,6)$ ，则以 $A B$ 为直径的圆的标准方程为 $\\qquad$ .\n\n#### 10.2.4 【 练 1-3\n\n正方形草地 $A B C D$ 边长 $1.2 ， E$ 到 $A B ， A D$ 距离为 $0.2 ， F$ 到 $B C ， C D$ 距离为 0.4 ，有个圆形通道经过 $E ， F$ ，且与 $A D$ 只有一个交点，求圆形通道的周长 $\\qquad$ . (精确到 $0.01)$\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-118.jpg?height=318&width=304&top__y=889&top__x=299","line":2226},{"title":"                                                             | 201x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=201&top__y=1293&top__x=738","line":2683,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 212x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=212&top__y=1513&top__x=723","line":2684,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 201x156","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=156&width=201&top__y=1742&top__x=738","line":2685,"embedded":true},{"title":"|401x429","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-161.jpg?height=429&width=401&top__y=982&top__x=468","line":3034,"embedded":true},{"title":"50,60$ ) 内的人数为 16 ，则下列结论正确的是（）\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-185.jpg?height=435&width=618&top__y=1781&top__x=296","line":3503}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1c51oxn","at":1771470854966}},"smart_blocks:20-Product/01-数学教学/讲义/09-讲义汇总/XDF讲义/FY25 高三数学秋季【行远班教材】修改版本.md#": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04605842,-0.00453407,0.06907953,-0.01689528,0.02922657,-0.00397077,-0.06272783,0.05607226,0.01539462,0.04050356,0.02663715,-0.08322488,0.03948841,0.00560387,0.00121823,-0.02159877,0.0459495,-0.04662105,-0.0506388,-0.01757422,0.13026845,-0.01316703,-0.01608669,-0.04954569,0.08143821,0.04524551,-0.00294503,-0.06151638,-0.02424893,-0.19356325,-0.00741796,0.06998642,0.05275537,0.04381003,0.03633552,-0.04864758,-0.01828294,0.04608708,-0.00994721,0.03681669,-0.00420634,0.0828274,-0.00723006,-0.00426016,0.00450922,-0.08402111,-0.0623056,-0.03096227,0.0426757,-0.00347673,-0.04318632,-0.02167105,0.00526341,0.02332473,-0.05023449,0.00282005,0.02557528,0.02154268,0.01427137,0.04308136,0.02540963,-0.00807473,-0.22192563,0.04650429,0.05000846,-0.02309498,-0.0295071,-0.04702266,0.02281937,0.0937872,-0.02135788,-0.01178477,-0.01700491,0.01189594,-0.00803717,-0.01891989,0.00473146,-0.09158169,-0.01657704,-0.05945169,-0.02120582,0.08418763,-0.02913041,0.00185699,0.00450512,0.04409035,0.00094766,-0.05003309,0.0209448,-0.05566061,0.00262404,-0.0233294,-0.01158606,0.00135642,-0.08167672,-0.04442016,0.03313569,0.02183543,-0.02534884,0.08758511,-0.04291717,0.02380751,0.04962266,-0.02151281,-0.04316134,0.01331935,-0.01257311,-0.06589152,-0.03461783,-0.0047559,0.0102124,-0.02318087,0.0929027,-0.03502811,-0.01764175,-0.00704546,-0.02524677,-0.02773153,-0.00866749,0.04026312,0.00759474,0.02506969,0.04087057,-0.0414908,0.00969525,-0.0272128,0.00853907,0.01068937,-0.01